roleExtraction.prompt:
Extract 5-8 key roles from this project description: {{projectDescription}}

Respond with only a JSON object in this exact format, no additional text:
{"roles": ["Role Name 1", "Role Name 2"]}

accountableResolution.prompt:
In a {{projectType}} project, which single role is most accountable for the task '{{task}}'?

Available roles: {{roles}}

Respond with only the exact role name from the list above. No explanation.

titleGeneration.prompt:
Write a concise, specific project title (4-7 words) for this project description:

{{projectDescription}}

Respond with only the title. No quotes, no punctuation at the end.

projectTypeClassification.prompt:
Classify this project description into one category: Mobile App, Web Redesign, CRM Migration, Marketing Campaign, Data Analytics, or Other.

{{projectDescription}}

Respond with only the category name.
